                        <interp inst="t18670128-219-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a previous conviction at Newington in 1861, to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. **—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18670128-219-punishment-23" type="punishmentDescription">
